oogle.com/chrome/answer/96816?hl=zh-Hant</a><br />\n<br />\n將書籤轉移到其他瀏覽器<br />\n<br />\n如果您決定改用其他瀏覽器，可以將 Chrome 保存的書籤全部轉移到新瀏覽器。<br />\n<br />\n在電腦上開啟 Chrome。<br />\n<br />\n按一下右上角的「更多」圖示&nbsp;￼。<br />\n<br />\n依序選取 [書籤]&nbsp;￼&nbsp;[書籤管理員]。<br />\n<br />\n依序按一下頂端的「更多」圖示&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;[匯出書籤]。<br />\n<br />\nChrome 會將您的書籤匯出成 HTML 檔案，您可以使用這個檔案將書籤匯入其他瀏覽器。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ntry try ok?"},{"pid":"1996483ea1f32e9bf1bc60476efdc0c7540ebb6d","tid":2157524,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"4b8ceafaa6f78fe937834577d78ca28be48dc2f3","tid":2157524,"uid":335235,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:57:08.000Z","msg":"唔係有得export?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T09:51:21.000Z","msg":"仲export<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩年代，自從chrome有得login google ac之後就cloud晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b435e400c0781267727949d97a44aa69d191c9","tid":2157524,"uid":66331,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1996483ea1f32e9bf1bc60476efdc0c7540ebb6d","tid":2157524,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"4b8ceafaa6f78fe937834577d78ca28be48dc2f3","tid":2157524,"uid":335235,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T05:57:08.000Z","msg":"唔係有得export?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T09:51:21.000Z","msg":"仲export<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩年代，自從chrome有得login google ac之後就cloud晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T10:06:55.000Z","msg":"慣咗export不過好麻煩<br />\n有咩事靠記憶del<br />\n<br />\n啱啱有sync果陣試過sync<br />\n無啦啦有日4000個bookmark變在8000<br />\n原來佢自動左<br />\n果次删到手軟<br />\n<br />\n從此唔敢再sync<br />\n到家陣都未明衰乜"},{"pid":"7a10bcafb936f04061ed19e049d34521ca647c4b","tid":2157524,"uid":160527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9b435e400c0781267727949d97a44aa69d191c9","tid":2157524,"uid":66331,"like":1,"disli