r />\n<br />\n<br />\ntry try ok?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:06:48.000Z","msg":"試左，係backup到，但排序亂晒，有無其他辦法？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ebe673fc6f3693355bde75f1a8f50dba6f336e1","tid":2157524,"uid":335235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:20:00.000Z","msg":"咁高要求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔識了"},{"pid":"963ca4168e37ee9528ca78cd236d333e0d112f10","tid":2157524,"uid":246694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:31:29.000Z","msg":"整多個ac 同步做back up la"},{"pid":"6d1ded1e189e410dc03f8a20589efa4d0f3a66bd","tid":2157524,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:43:22.000Z","msg":"早2日換新腦<br />\n冇做任何backup<br />\nd書籤全部出現番晒<br />\n應該login左google就全部落番晒黎"},{"pid":"51bf8c3fb11c7d9ab642ce68b52b0a4e55665de4","tid":2157524,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d1ded1e189e410dc03f8a20589efa4d0f3a66bd","tid":2157524,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:43:22.000Z","msg":"早2日換新腦<br />\n冇做任何backup<br />\nd書籤全部出現番晒<br />\n應該login左google就全部落番晒黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:45:32.000Z","msg":"不過駛唔駛sync或者其他野先做到就唔肯定了"}]}